faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d405be9e9f1dbe00ca7b06b1bb897fe171847eaa","tid":2456082,"uid":60057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T01:51:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">美國華盛頓一名移民顧問 Cris Ram&oacute;n 認為，拜登政府推行正面人道措施，但墨西哥就要做骯髒工作 (dirty work)，形容拜登政府就像要做「好人」，但墨西哥人就要扮演「醜人」。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢句屌得好，偽君子黎。要人地國家禁自己國民/誇境難民走，你自己國家就無掩雞籠咁但又叫人唔好黎，你玩撚晒啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過老實講，夠無恥先可以同支共鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過前題係佢唔奶先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f20f5dc75dd98e20444532851e399eb8790443","tid":2456082,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T02:18:47.000Z","msg":"敖狗有冇講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d272200d820ddf8952fb1b0dcc51466640d8301","tid":2456082,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T02:19:43.000Z","msg":"Mexician lives matter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}